OL,2,Q=$j#!7 /m|j#!wjk5w   S #z7   
OL,3,Q}|j|4} |~j|4}|jj5}|   S j7    
OL,4, ````````````````````````````   S h4    
OL,5,E"IT'S YOUR WILDLIFE...SAVE IT"         
OL,7,BIf you're a self-proclaimed eco-       
OL,8,Bconscious,Ewildlife expertBwho's proud 
OL,9,Bto be green, think twice before you    
OL,10,Bholler your attributes to the world... 
OL,12,B"Make sure you've got the know-how to  
OL,13,Bback your claims," says a spokesman    
OL,14,BfromELondon Zoo.                       
OL,16,E"Ninety-five per centBof self-professed
OL,17,Bgreen-thinking people we quizzed in a  
OL,18,Brecent survey didn't have a clue about 
OL,19,Btheir native species - shame on them!" 
OL,20, ``````````````````````````````````1/6``
OL,21, C        by Bernadette Carroll         
OL,22,A]GM  FOR THE LATEST GREEN NEWS p161    
OL,24,AWrite It!   BFun&Games   CGoss   FTV   
PN,14802
SC,0002
FL,149,150,143,110,1ff,101
OL,1,Q?/`pp0ppp ?/`pp0ppp`pp0ppp   S ~o}   
OL,2,Q=$j#!7 /m|j#!wjk5w   S #z7   
OL,3,Q}|j|4} |~j|4}|jj5}|   S j7    
OL,4, ````````````````````````````   S h4    
OL,5,E"IT'S YOUR WILDLIFE...SAVE IT"         
OL,7,BWhen askedEhow many types of reptiles  
OL,8,Eexist in the UKB 53% of visitors to    
OL,9,BLondon Zoo guessed at anything from 150
OL,10,Bto 2,000 - only one person gave the    
OL,11,Bright answer -Bone!                    
OL,13,BIn response to the question:EWhat      
OL,14,Eanimals live in the UK and shouldn't?B-
OL,15,Banswers ranged from pumas to wallabies.
OL,17,BIndeed one visitor was convinced a     
OL,18,BpreviouslyEunheard-of speciesBcalled   
OL,19,B"shiny snakes" were found in the UK.   
OL,20, ``````````````````````````````````2/6``
OL,21,C  Go GreenG160      C  Green NewsG161  
