OL,1,Q?/`pp0ppp ?/`pp0ppp`pp0ppp   S ~o}   
OL,2,Q=$j#!7 /m|j#!wjk5w   S #z7   
OL,3,Q}|j|4} |~j|4}|jj5}|   S j7    
OL,4, ````````````````````````````   S h4    
OL,5,E"IT'S YOUR WILDLIFE...SAVE IT"         
OL,7,BThe London Zoo survey which is part of 
OL,8,BtheEBritish Zoo Federation's national  
OL,9,Ecampaign,BIt's Your Wildlife...Save It,
OL,10,Bwas designed to show that wildlife is  
OL,11,Bthreatened in the UK.                  
OL,13,B"Half of the people we questioned      
OL,14,Ecouldn't name one species that's       
OL,15,Eendangered in the UK,"Bsays a somewhat 
OL,16,Bshocked spokeswoman from the Zoo.      
OL,18,B"Yet they could all name species like  
OL,19,EtigersBwhich are not native to the UK."
OL,20, ``````````````````````````````````3/6``
