OL,1,Q?/`pp0ppp ?/`pp0ppp`pp0ppp   S ~o}   
OL,2,Q=$j#!7 /m|j#!wjk5w   S #z7   
OL,3,Q}|j|4} |~j|4}|jj5}|   S j7    
OL,4, ````````````````````````````   S h4    
OL,5,E"IT'S YOUR WILDLIFE...SAVE IT"         
OL,7,BThe It's Your Wildlife...Save It       
OL,8,Bcampaign aims to get the public to take
OL,9,Bresponsibility for the nation's        
OL,10,Bwildlife by signingEpledges.           
OL,12,BA spokeswoman from London Zoo says:    
OL,13,B"Once signed, you're under oath to do  
OL,14,Ball sorts of things that will help the 
OL,15,Benvironment likeEturning off the tap   
OL,16,Ewhen brushing your teeth.              
OL,18,B"This will help conserve water which is
OL,19,Bvital forElocal eco-systems."          
OL,20, ``````````````````````````````````5/6``
