OL,2,Q=$j#!7 /m|j#!wjk5w   S #z7   
OL,3,Q}|j|4} |~j|4}|jj5}|   S j7    
OL,4, ````````````````````````````   S h4    
OL,5,E"IT'S YOUR WILDLIFE...SAVE IT"         
OL,7,BIt's Your Wildlife...Save It pledges   
OL,8,Bcost #2 each - the British Zoo         
OL,9,BFederation, organisers of the          
OL,10,Binitiative aim to raiseE#120,000 for   
OL,11,Ewildlife projects around Britain.      
OL,13,BA spokesman from London Zoo says: "It's
OL,14,Bimportant that we help conservation    
OL,15,Bprojects overseas - but we musn't      
OL,16,Bforget theEproblems on our own shores."
OL,18,EBIf you would like to sign a pledge   
OL,19, B callE0171 449 6231.                  
